Description: Come take a look at the 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in Vancouver, WA! The open concept in the kitchen and living room is perfect for comfortable living. The kitchen features appliances, countertops, and pantry space. The primary bedroom has laminate floors, closet space, and a half bath. Venture into the backyard with yard space for entertaining. Ideal location to parks, stores, and restaurants!

Stunning single level, 3 bed, 1.75 bath ranch in the desirable Northwest neighborhood. You will love the flow of this home with a large living area featuring a gas fireplace, Formal dining with another gas fireplace and large skylight to brighten up the room. Could also be used as second great room, you decide! Updated kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar, New roof and gutters, fresh interior & exterior paint, new range hood, new toilets and so much more! Tons of windows throughout filling this home with natural light. Make sure to view full list of upgrades attached. Large private fenced back yard with fire pit. Professionally landscaped front & back yards are ready for entertaining! This is the one!

This solid and well maintained home is ready for you! The long-time owner has decided to hang his hat on being a landlord, but not before spending months of his time and considerable expense in making sure that the turn-key finished product meets his high standards.  A newer roof, new flooring, and fresh paint inside and out just to start. The home has good space with 2 bedrooms on the main level and a large bonus room upstairs, great curb appeal, and it sets in a quiet residential area just 4 minutes away from I-5. The home also has it's own septic, which will save you money on your monthly bills. This is a great home, and an excellent value.

address: 8037 Valley Rd NE, Moses Lake, WA 98837
Description: Remodeled 4 bedroom 2 bathroom with an attached studio apartment available on Valley Rd in Moses Lake. Exterior features include: fresh exterior paint, 2 car finished garage, large back patio with railing, covered side patio with built in BBQ and entertaining area, fenced backyard, underground sprinkler system, large detached storage shed, large side lot for RV/boat storage or potential shop, lake and park views from backyard. Interior features include: new laminate flooring throughout living/dining/kitchen area, new carpet in bedrooms, wood fireplace on main floor, natural stone accents throughout, jetted tub with tile surround, open concept kitchen, fresh paint throughout, one bedroom studio apartment attached to home, central heat/air.

address: 4359 Grouse Creek Rd, Loon Lake, WA 99148
Description: Oasis in the Woods! What a peaceful getaway nestled beneath the rolling hills of treed forest land. Situated on over 20 acres just North of Deer Lake, this gem of the forest does not disappoint! Huge 30x40 shop with loft apartment and separate kitchen, bath and laundry has plenty of room to store all of your toys. If you're looking for serenity, there's a gurgling creek that runs on the property, and a deck off the back for those outdoor summer evenings. This home has recently had several updates, including new flooring throughout, fresh paint, new doors and interior trim, new levelor blinds, new fixtures and ceiling fans and lots of tender loving care. There are several outbuildings, including a greenhouse, two carports, ample open space parking, additional storage sheds - and room to build more! Although the hard stuff has already been done for you, there's still lots of opportunity to add your own personalized touches.

Cute bungalow home on large R-2 lot. 2BR/1BA on main floor along with kitchen, living and dining room. Tons of storage. Small basement with laundry, 1/2 bath and bedroom. Sunroom/hot tub room. Fenced backyard. Fresh paint on main floor, new flooring in kitchen.

This bright and open split-level features beautifully updated finishes throughout the home while sitting on a quiet dead-end street that backs up to a protected greenbelt. Fabulous location, yet still tucked away! Minutes from Whole Foods, shopping, dining, schools and new light rail! Upstairs boasts refinished original hardwoods, 3 beds, open concept kitchen + dining + living room. Enjoy 2 wood burning fireplace w/new mantle and tile surround upstairs. Fresh paint throughout, updated windows and new carpet downstairs. Refreshed bathrooms with tile + new glazed tub in full bath. 4th bed downstairs w/laundry and rec room. Oversized 1 car garage. Large private backyard with deck and covered porch for year round enjoyment.

Charming light & bright home in the highly desired Seven Oaks! You'll love the open-concept feel with tons of natural light, beautiful LVP floors, & recessed lighting! Spacious Family room has a cozy gas fireplace with stylish mantel, & French Doors! Stunning Modern Kitchen has tile granite counters, bay window, breakfast bar, custom tile backsplash, SS appliances & plenty of storage! Outdoors has a large yard & deck, perfect for entertaining year round; a garden area, & fully fenced yard! Stylish Primary Suite has a window seat and a walk-in closet. 2 additional bedrooms on the upper level. Other features include: New carpet on the upper level, fresh paint throughout, 2 car garage, RV parking, & easy access to highways & Seven oaks park!

Great rambler with lots of updates. Mature trees surround just over 10,000 sqft level lot. Warm and inviting with plush new carpet and flooring throughout, wood burning stove is highlighted with wood feature wall in living room. There is fresh paint inside and out along with new trim, light fixtures, doors, and updated bathrooms. Your kitchen has brand new appliances that have never been used and french doors that lead you to your new deck overlooking fully fenced yard. Full separate studio w/ skylights out back. More updates include; new washer/dryer, hot water tank, garage door and opener, two new wall heaters, & a new electrical panel. Easy access to i5 and 525, hwy 99,  Stickney Lake, Paine field & Boeing, parks, stores & amenities.

Delightful home on beautiful Anderson Island. Don't let the 1994 build date deter you. This home has been well maintained. No squeaks, no leaks! New roof 3 years ago, fresh interior paint, new mini blinds, new keyed-alike locks, newer W/D. Home standby generator. PLUS it's fully furnished, turnkey; just move right in!  Convenient circular floor plan with large kitchen and living room. Main bedroom en suite. Large deck in private back yard. 20 x 10 storage shed has a freezer that stays. Metal carport cover. Short distance to Riviera park on Lake Josephine. All Riviera Community Club amenities: tennis court, fresh and salt water boat launches, clubhouse, golf course, swimming beaches. Only 20 minutes from Steilacoom on Pierce County Ferry.

Totally updated to taste! Quartz countertops highlight the kitchen with undermount sink and new stainless steel appliances, such a great place to cook those family or single meals. New Luxury Vinyl Plank in the living and dining areas bring that touch of class and durability. Warm up around the new gas stove highlighting the living room. With new carpeting in the bedrooms you are sure to keep those tootsies warm. The bathroom also features quartz and undermount sink with new vinyl flooring.

Fantastic home with room for everyone. 5+ bedrooms, 3 bathrooms with a 2 story living room, big rec room, media room & pass through office/den. Home has all new carpet & tile flooring, granite in kitchen & baths. New high end appliances, lighting, hardware & handrails on both decks. Fresh exterior paint. Main suite seperate from the rest with a big soaking tub, 5' shower & walk-in closet. All the brs are good sized and have cable. High speed internet that many can use at the same time. Lots of great storage. 2 heat systems, 2 septics, 2 electric panels w/ extra room if you want to add a shop. All closets have lighting. Leased propane tank for the fireplace & kitchen range. UG sprinklers in front yard. Cyclone fenced in backyard has lawn, balance in back ready for your landscaping or garden

MLS# 258535 The love that went into this home can be seen from the curb. Located in West Pasco's growing community and two blocks from Sunny Meadows Park, is your new smart home. Wired with a complete smart system, you can walk in your new home and ask Google to turn on your lights, or even ask Google to change your kitchen under cabinet and to e-kick lighting. Brand new paint inside and out, this home was renovated to be treated as a new home. The home with a two-year old HVAC system, includes all new flooring with carpet in the four bedrooms. There is also a mudroom that is a huge bonus that can also be used for a bedroom or office. The can lighting throughout the living room, kitchen, and hallway light up the beautifully done details that were added to this home. The new kitchen was designed with a family who needs pantry space, and the modern fixtures match the bathrooms beautifully. The backyard was completely resurfaced, includes concreted patio areas, and underground sprinklers in both the back and front yards. The west side of the home includes a space to parkyour RV. This home is a must see.

address: 667 Woodland Loop NE, Ocean Shores, WA 98569
Description: Move-in ready home with great use of space! Just a short distance to shopping, North Bay Park, & the sandy beaches of Ocean Shores! Main floor primary bdrm w/walk-in closet & attached bath. Second large main floor bdrm has walk-in closet.  Upstairs you will find a huge bdrm that would make a great home office. Linen closet & full bathroom in the entry hall. Great room has a propane fireplace in the living room area, spacious kitchen, walk-in pantry, laundry room w/door leading to the attached garage. Fresh paint throughout & some updates in both bathrooms. Fenced backyard has a giant deck for gathering &  plenty of space. You'll love the remote fireplace,  great floorplan & so much more. Call today !

This duplex style condo was architecturally designed by the original owner to look and feel like a large residence rather than a typical duplex. One unit is slightly larger than the other. Unit 6421 is approx.1875 SF and unit 6419 is approx. 1650SF. Both units feature an open floor plan and multiple outdoor spaces to include a deck off the master bedroom and a large, covered patio off the kitchen and living room. Fresh paint in and out with all new flooring and other updates as well. This sale includes both units and is also listed as a duplex but is legally recorded as 2 condos with separate tax parcels. photos are of Unit 6421 but representative of finishes thru out. 4/6 beds, 6 baths, 4 car garage represent the counts for both units.

Come and see this fantastic 4 bedroom house/ professional office space!  Recently updated with high-efficiency mini splits (stay warm in the winter and cool in the summer!), new carpet, new vinyl flooring and fresh paint. The current configuration is set up for professional use, with a reception area, 4 individual offices as well as a kitchen and half bath. Located ideally for anyone looking for quick access to highway 167, downtown kent, the bus line, the train, you name it! New owners can convert half bath back to full bath pretty easily.

Spacious updated 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Tri Level with new roof and fresh paint! Remodeled Kitchen with new range/oven, tile floors, new trim, new countertops and walk-in pantry. Vaulted, open floorplan with slider to covered back deck. Basement family room, laundry & half bath. 2 Car attached garage. Gas heat & ceiling fans. Fenced backyard with raised garden beds. Lakefront community with beach access and clubhouse. Highly rated Tahoma School District.

One owner home, 4 bedrooms, 1.5 baths.2500 sq. ft.  Seven month renovation 2021. Custom Wrought Iron gate.  Pears, apples, cherries. New 70 foot front deck. New rear deck, ADA ramp. The pine paneled cathedral ceiling invites you into a well lit living room with best Blaze King airtight wood stove. New paint, gutters and snow stops, skylights, dish washer, faucets, lighting inside and out. Old growth Doug fir doors and trim.  Huge walk in pantry, 15 y/0 Snap loc metal roof. 40x40 RV shed W/hookups. 36x60 shop with 720 sq. ft. loft.Laundry with 25 ft counter space, and drain. New Septic system in 2021 The new owner will have access to the community waterfront built for the community water system, look at the photos of river and clubhouse !!!!

~ clean and move in ready, new carpet, tile, fresh paint. This 2 BRM 1 BATH 14 x 70 Mobile home is in desirable 55 Senior Park Sonary Crest (Space rent is $535 and is subject to change. All buyers to be park approved.) Bathroom has a garden tub and separate shower. Furnace is newer. Large Livingroom is bright and fresh new paint and brand new carpet.

address: 2611 S 288th St UNIT 28, Federal Way, WA 98003
Description: Well maintained 2 bed 2 bath home in Parkwood Lane. 55+ gated community close to shops, restaurants, parks, and freeway access. Brand new wall to wall carpet, fresh paint, and open floor plan ready for all of your finishing touches. Full master suite with connected master bath includes tub, shower, and plenty of closet space. Breakfast nook, dining area, high ceilings and plenty of room to stretch out and relax. Low maintenance yard, carport with garage storage, and perfect size back for a small dog and sitting in the sun. A Must See!

Immaculate park with no age restrictions! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath. With a private back yard, two sheds for storage! Home features open floor plan concept, with a nice size remodled kitchen, large living room, master suite with a remodeled master bath. Home has all new flooring in every room, remodeled master bath and guest bath, lots of windows for natural light. It is a must see!!! walk-in closet.

address: 201 Union Ave SE UNIT 135, Renton, WA 98059
Description: New Improved Price! Lovely 2 bed 2 bath home in the quiet and desirable 55+ Leisure Estates park. Corner unit provides rare pull through parking with carport and plenty of outdoor space. Fresh landscaping, attached storage and fresh updates like paint and flooring. Kitchen opens to family room and includes new appliances. Large living room and dining area with built in shelving. Two primary bedrooms, oversized mud room with laundry. All appliances stay.

This property has it all!! Nice house + Large Barn + Large Shop + beautiful 9.77-acre rolling pastures w/white fencing!! The 3-bed, 2.5-bath move-in-ready home has fresh paint, new carpet, new flooring & new fixtures! An add'l room is perfect for a game rm, toy rm, theater rm. All bedrooms are spacious. This sturdy equestrian facility was built to last: horizontal 2x4s, 13+ stalls, tack room, grooming stall, wash rack, feed rm, foaling stall, amazing loft w/stairs for plenty of hay storage, covered shavings bin--all just waiting to be brought back to a working facility. Check out the simply amazing shop: 1440 sf w/work bench, bathrm, RV pkg w/septic hook-up or RV dump. Dream it, visualize & bring it to life exactly the way you want it!

Fresh updates adorn this 2 bedroom 2 bath manufactured home with carport, covered porches. Heat pump, washer and dryer included. Easy to care for exterior siding is vinyl, low maintenance yard and cement pad for your own garden shed.  Fresh paint inside and new flooring. The park allows for 1 small pet. Sans Souci is a 55 + community. Please get preapproval with the park. Park lease fee includes garbage, septic,yard waste removal, and comcast with 3 cable boxes and 130 channels.  The community center is open for some functions currently, pool tables and other games. Heated pool during summer for residents. Fresh, ready to move in home light and bright. Located near shopping, freeways and medical facilities.

Super cute and turn key! This modified single wide with addition has been remodeled and is ready for you to move in and enjoy life! Featuring 3 beds 1 & 3/4 bath, spacious living room, adorable kitchen and good sized dining room are for entertaining! All new kitchen cabinets, counters, appliances, flooring, and fresh paint! Huge fenced yard with garden area, 3 outbuildings for extra storage and a place to park your car. Located in Curlew with a partial view of the Kettle River this home is a perfect starter home or if you are looking to downsize!

Tall Firs 55+ community invites you to this luxury condo with two oversized bedrooms. Perfect location and move in ready. Completely updated inside and out. Newer roof, fresh exterior paint, newer windows, updated flooring throughout, remodeled kitchen with new cabinets and granite counters, trex deck and more. Walk outside to your beautifully landscaped yard with large deck and firepit; great for entertaining. This home has additional parking for guests as well as covered carport and additional storage. Home also includes air conditioning. Community offers RV parking and clubhouse. Easy access to Meridian, freeways, golf course, and restaurants. This is a must see home, don't miss out. Call for a private showing.

Expansive sound, mountain and sunset views. This fully & freshly updated Studio Condo has much to boast. The Modern style unit features an updated kitchen, complete w/SS appliances, & subway tile backsplash. Gleaming LVP flooring, fresh paint & new millwork/fixtures throughout the rest of unit lead to a beautifully updated bathroom. Murphy bed allows for open space when hosting friends or family & ground floor unit makes it easy to access. Perfectly located near the waterfront, beach park, farmer's market, restaurants & shops. Great Des Moines community with easy access to freeways, light rail, Sea-Tac airport & Seattle. Low HOA dues that include water/sewer/garbage. Tired of paying rent? This studio has it all!
